Applies to backend logging only:

Logging is imported from "@/logging" [index.ts](mdc:lib/logging/index.ts)

First argument must be an object of log details, second argument is a text name for the log.

Error logs must have an error key { error: inspect(error) } using the nodejs inspect utility.